          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLLOrmQGvylLNbyu7AiP2g0v492hABTLnzEuwTJbPndX-ONlQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100",
          "description": "If you have 20 mins to wait for someone to unlock the cases then this is a great option. If you don\u2019t plan on moving in to the store it\u2019s faster to walk over to another location than wait here. Can\u2019t even get cotton swabs without having a case unlocked. Find a better business model.",
