          "description": "Bought haircare color product that turned out to be tampered with.  When I opened the box, some items were missing and the contents of applicator bottle had been replaced by an unknown, discolored,  vile smelling, emulsified fluid.  This was both disgusting and alarming.  Staff was very polite and helpful when I returned the tampered box for a full refund.  I suggested they check their CTV to find the culprit responsible as I had made the purchase only the day prior.",
