        {
          "username": "Sara Doe",
          "rating": 1,
          "contributor_id": "118424892787503261290",
          "user_review_count": 7,
          "user_photo_count": 3,
          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKthXbw15F6BlZL81a2TN2A9K46l90_NX6qy_SDWG2h8-dyVA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100",
          "description": "Quite possibly the most uncaring group of pharmacist I\u2019ve ever had the displeasure of having to deal with. I\u2019ve been trying to refill a necessary to my livelihood medication that I got monthly for the past 10 years of my life for over five weeks now and I have been nothing But patient over the phone and in person they will not give you the time of day. When I show up in person to try to get the medication, they just told me \u201coh we don\u2019t have that\u201d. Not and I\u2019m sorry not we can try to get that to you soon. \u201cI don\u2019t have it\u201c and when I say, when will you have it because it\u2019s been over a month of me trying to refill it they said that my doctor would have to put in a new prescription. I let them know my doctor has done that every week for the past month trying to get this medication filled for me. I truly think these people do not care whatsoever for the patients. Single Worst pharmacy I\u2019ve ever encountered.",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21jMk5YSXhaVFJRTnpWYWRqbFBWMmMwYTNWTmVWRRAB!2m1!1s0x0:0x7f8fc547df25198b!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOmc2NXIxZTRQNzVadjlPV2c0a3VNeVE%7C%7C?hl=en",
          "date": "10 months ago",
          "date_iso8601": "2025-08-20T21:53:10+00:00"
        },
        {
          "username": "Brooke Peterson",
          "rating": 1,
          "contributor_id": "108701324862518158865",
          "user_review_count": 14,
          "user_photo_count": 0,
          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW1EmyR6UdggI_olSTYzsUyvTfuGZ9Ai7PAS9qFu_kWoRzq3anO=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100",
          "description": "This place is a hot piece of garbage. NEVER get your prescriptions here. I got a prescription for 30 pills and they miscounted, gave me 17, and refused to acknowledge their mistake. They also told me that in order to get the remaining I\u2019d need another prescription from the doctor, and even then, it wouldn\u2019t be covered by insurance. I\u2019m so beyond disappointed. Will absolutely NEVER be coming here again.",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJMjJrWWU2d3RxT2NBEAE!2m1!1s0x0:0x7f8fc547df25198b!3m1!1s2@1:CIHM0ogKEI22kYe6wtqOcA%7C%7C?hl=en",
