          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWA8Z2mS39GzQC3T3bsYpnkMVxgYKNMVmb9sNfiDJiN0gEMNKNxtQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100",
          "description": "At 6:30 pm i picked up my \"T\"prescription b/c tomorrow I\u2019m having cardiac surgery . I also went to retrieve a fast Healthy Choice dinner which required help unlocking the freezer. Terra responded to my ring and mumbled something and walked away. I rang again and she returned loudly scolding me for ringing again. I explained I didnt understand why she was yelling at me and I pointed to the HC Beef Merlot dinner and she opened the wrong cabinet. When I corrected her she yelled at me again that I had pointed at the wrong cabinet. I asked her to lower her voice and she scolded me a third time saying \u201cI don\u2019t want to talk to you anymore I just want to get out of here \u201c. Then she opened the right cabinet and I silently walked away and bought milk and nuts too. Terra is still there, me more rarely. Be careful.",
